summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Animal Image Similarity Search application. All backend APIs working correctly (9/9 tests passed). Frontend UI fully functional with proper navigation, search interface, dataset management, analytics, and settings. Integration between frontend and backend working excellently.
passed_tests: Dataset Stats API - returns 10 images, 5 categories, index built status
Categories API - returns 5 categories (cat, dog, elephant, lion, tiger)
Sample Categories API - returns 30 sample animal categories
Logs API - retrieves activity logs correctly
Clear Logs API - successfully clears logs
Upload Dataset API - successfully uploads images with category
Build Index API - builds FAISS index successfully
Search API - finds similar images in 182ms with proper results
Frontend app loading and header display
Search tab UI elements (query panel, results panel, sliders)
Dataset tab functionality (upload panel, stats, category selection)
Analytics tab display (shows 'Run a search' message before search)
Settings tab model information (ResNet50, IndexFlatIP badges)
Activity logs panel with expand/collapse functionality
Clear logs functionality with toast notification
